    "        \"AdamW + Cosine is superior\",\n",
    "        \"Specificity shows highest variance\"\n",
    "    ],\n",
    "    \"Recommendation\": [\n",
    "        \"Use standard augmentation\",\n",
    "        \"Can train effectively with 50% data\",\n",
    "        \"Consider removing attention\",\n",
    "        \"Use 256×256 when possible\",\n",
    "        \"Use AdamW + Cosine annealing\",\n",
    "        \"Use ensemble to stabilize performance\"\n",
    "    ]\n",
    "}\n",
    "\n",
    "df_summary = pd.DataFrame(summary_data)\n",
    "display(df_summary)\n",
    "\n",
    "save_results({\"ablation_summary\": df_summary.to_dict(orient=\"records\")}, \"ablation_summary\", \"../results\")\n",
    "print(\"Final ablation summary saved.\")"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "## Final Recommendations\n",
    "\n",
    "- Use **standard augmentation**, **256×256 resolution**, and **AdamW + CosineAnnealing** for best performance.\n",
    "- Consider removing the attention module for simplicity and similar results.\n",
    "- Use **ensemble** of multiple seeds to stabilize specificity.\n",
    "- The model is robust to reduced training data thanks to transfer learning."
   ]
  }
